snippet.textDisplay:
Apart from Faakhir's part, the rest of the song is simply brilliant. Faakhir has done great job in making the music. But his pronunciation take away the essence of the song a littler bit. A Pukhto singer would have done it with perfection. Nonetheless, great effort in music because I loved the assembling of music. Overall, a lovely song. Loved it. Zeb is so charming and fluent. And the music, simply brilliant. 10 on 10.
Thank you Coke Studio for doing a Pukhto song.
Truly, sound of the nation.
